    &lt;form method="post"&gt;
        {% csrf_token %}
        {{ form.as_p }}
        &lt;button type="submit"&gt;Guardar Cambios&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/form&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
Paso 3: Configurar las URLs
